page.title: 13OH-BUOY
page.content: Mr and Mrs Whithers have lived in Woodland road,in a house called{ {OH-BUOY}which they made six years ago.But they own the next house to them.They've lived there for over 26 years altogether. The old man's house was made in 1834 by a man called{Stuggie,}a well known Bristol builder.He had a hull of a boat roughly 20ft long.He also had timber shed around the side of the house,they have a big conservatory. They have two dogs called Jotti and Tucker. The family originally came from Derby and he makes all kinds of models in workshop. His best known train is {Bournemouth {Bell}because he used to travel on it a lot before.They both saw{Halleys Comet the last time it came round{75 years ago. {IAIN ELD
